				\begin{document}$$\% {\text{ DPPH percentage}}\, = \,\left[ {\left( {{\text{A}}0 - {\text{A1}}} \right)/{\text{A}}0} \right] \, \times { 1}00$$\end{document}%DPPH percentage=A0-A1/A0×100
